description: Outcrop Silver & Gold Corporation engages in the acquisition and exploration of mineral properties in Colombia. It primarily explores for gold, silver, and copper deposits. The company's flagship property is the Santa Ana project covering an area of approximately 25,000 hectares located in northern Tolima Department, Colombia. The company was formerly known as Outcrop Gold Corp. and changed its name to Outcrop Silver & Gold Corporation in June 2021. Outcrop Silver & Gold Corporation was founded in 1993 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
